<section class="entry-content">
<p>A nice bit of casual sexism on James Martin&#8217;s Food Map of Britain on the Good Food channel just now:</p>
<p>&#8216;I&#8217;ve yet to meet an Irishman who doesn&#8217;t love his spuds&#8217; (or words to that effect). So only Irishmen eat potatoes then, Mr Martin? Dude, I think you&#8217;ll find you mean that you&#8217;ve yet to meet an Irish PERSON who doesn&#8217;t love THEIR spuds!</p>
